Summary: lights at night unknown under tree debris behind backyard
divs: Sighting DetailsProperty behind house (wooded area) was recently sold to unknown owner. Heard from a neighbor that it was supposed to be a parking lot for buses and other equipment. Its evidently unfinished but end of it looks like a UFO landing area. Noticed when I come home from work to feed dogs at night unkwown lights under tree debris at creek behind house. I will not approach not knowing what to expect. Does not look like anyting I've ever seen (like an animal habitat). Please respond to let me know if you've had any similar cases.
